                                    <p>Notwithstanding anything stated elsewhere in this Agreement, the Lender may, subject to Applicable Law, at any time, in its discretion, cancel the undisbursed amount of Loan without prior notice to the Borrower and in such event, if required by the Lender, the Outstanding Amount shall be payable by the Borrower within fifteen (15) days of being so called upon, to the Lender without any delay or demur. </p>

