                                <ol>
                                    <li>If due date of a loan account is March 31, 2021, and full dues are not received before the
                                        Lender runs the day-end process for this date, the date of overdue shall be March 31, 2021. If
                                        it continues to remain overdue, then this account shall get tagged as SMA1 upon running day-end
                                        process on April 30, 2021 i.e. upon completion of 30 days of being continuously overdue.
                                        Accordingly, the date of SMA-1 classification for that account shall be April 30, 2021.</li>
                                    <li>Similarly, if the account continues to remain overdue, it shall get tagged as SMA-2 upon running
                                        day-end process on May 30, 2021 and if continues to remain overdue further, it shall get
                                        classified as NPA upon running day end process on June 29, 2021.</li>
                                </ol>
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                    </td>
                </tr>
